args.code:
from PyPDF2 import PdfReader

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/5-SimPO/SimPO/paper.pdf'
reader = PdfReader(pdf_path)

# Try to extract the first 5 pages for SimPO loss description
text = ''
for i, page in enumerate(reader.pages[:5]):
    text += page.extract_text() + '\n\n'

# Print a snippet to check if extraction works
print(text[:2000])
